### Steps API Test Examples
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Sign up a customer first (if you don't have an account)
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/customers/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890"
}

### 2. Login to get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/customers/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###############################################
### STEPS API ENDPOINTS
###############################################

### 3. Sync steps for a specific date
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "2026-02-23",
  "steps": 8500
}

### 4. Sync steps for another date
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "2026-02-22",
  "steps": 10000
}

### 5. Update steps for existing date (will upsert)
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "2026-02-23",
  "steps": 12000
}

### 6. Get today's steps
GET {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get steps for a date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/range?from=2026-02-20&to=2026-02-25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get steps for a week
GET {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/range?from=2026-02-17&to=2026-02-23
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###############################################
### ERROR CASES
###############################################

### Missing date
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "steps": 5000
}

### Invalid date format
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "23-02-2026",
  "steps": 5000
}

### Negative steps
POST {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "date": "2026-02-23",
  "steps": -100
}

### Missing query parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/range?from=2026-02-20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Invalid date range (from > to)
GET {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/range?from=2026-02-25&to=2026-02-20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### No authentication token
GET {{baseUrl}}/fitness/steps/today
